A cikin wani shahidi mai sha'awar, Kavanaugh ya ce ya tabbata cewa hakan ba zai faru ba.
Nielsen ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a cewa mutane sama da miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan bidiyon.
Kamfanin ya ba da rahoton matsakaicin sauraro a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a nan take ba ne don sauran tashoshin da suka sake watsa shi, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen tana da matsala wajen auna yawan mutanen da suke kallon talabijin daga ofisoshin.
