Trump ya yi zabensa a Virginia a tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan da Trump ya shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da zanga-zangar da zai yi a garuruwan da ke kusa da shi kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da shi don ya cika matsayin da ake da shi a Kotun Koli, Trump na neman samun goyon baya a zaben rabin lokaci na gaba, saboda 'yan Republican suna fuskantar haɗarin rasa ikon Majalisar Dokoki lokacin da aka jefa kuri'a a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai faru a West Virginia, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon taron a Intanet?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018 a karfe 7 na yamma.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana game da batun shari'ar da ake yi a wannan makon ga dan takarar Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai matukar damuwa game da zargin lalata da kuma dakatar da zaben amincewa da majalisar dattijai na mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican su fuskanci zaben Nuwamba da sabon ƙarfi.
Saboda haka, taron tarurruka guda biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, an yi niyyar "karfafawa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa da majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga tsarinsa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin yakin neman zaben", wani mai magana da yawun Trump ya shaida wa Reuters wanda ya fi son kada a nada shi.
Taron da za a yi a Wesbanco Stadium a daren yau zai iya kawo masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania tare da samun labarai daga Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a wata da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya samu sama da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Jam'iyyar Republican ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya kasance na karshe a cikin binciken.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya goyi bayan shi a cikin binciken ba", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, ga Reuters.
