Turai ta yi wasa mafi kyau a matsayin tawagar har zuwa yanzu kuma suna da babbar fa'ida a ranar ƙarshe, amma wannan zaman na foursomes ya kuma nuna cewa Team USA na da ƙarfin gwiwa don yaƙi, wani abu da wasu, musamman Stateside, suka yi shakkar.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder.
Turai za ta yi nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan ta fita daga cikin 'yan wasan hudu da hudu da kuma ta fi Amurka 10-6 a gaba.
Ƙungiyar mai ban sha'awa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci nauyin da suka yi nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods wanda ke fama da matsala don tashi da maki hudu a cikin Le Golf National.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, wadda ke neman ta ci gaba da lashe kofin da ta yi shekaru biyu a Hazeltine, ta ci nasara a kan ƙungiyar Amurka da ta gaza a wasan safe, ta ci wasan 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a cikin hudu, ta ci wasanni huɗu, amma ba ta iya rage fa'idar ba.
A ranar Lahadi, 'yan wasan Jim Furyk sun bukaci maki takwas daga cikin wasannin da suka buga domin su ci gaba da lashe kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon ɗan Turai na farko da ya ci maki huɗu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, mai suna Molliwood, bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, su ne ma'aurata na biyu da suka ci maki huɗu daga farkon wasannin huɗu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin fourballs, sun dace daidai don doke Woods mai lalata da kuma sabon ɗan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau tare da 5 & 4 mafi mahimmanci.
Woods, wanda ya buga wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar ba tare da jin tausayi ko ɗaukaka ba, ya nuna wasu abubuwan ban mamaki, amma yanzu ya rasa wasanni 19 daga 29 a cikin wasanni na fourballs da foursomes da biyar a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta a wasan safiya, ya sake haɗuwa da abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a cikin foursomes yana cin nasara a kan Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, lambobin duniya na ɗaya da na uku.
Turai ba zai iya ci gaba da samun nasara a kan wani m iska rana a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa maki na biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun samu nasara 2&1 akan Mutanen Espanya John Rahm da Ian Poulter a cikin fourballs kuma sun sake cin nasarar Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a cikin foursomes bayan sun rasa ramukan farko biyu.
Akwai sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup inda ƙungiyar ta ci gaba da maki huɗu a cikin mutum, kodayake a matsayin mai riƙe da kyautar yanzu, ƙungiyar Furyk kawai ta buƙaci daidaitawa don kiyaye shi.
Amma bayan da ya yi nasara a matsayi na biyu a cikin kwanaki biyu, ya yi kama da cewa ya yi nasara a ranar Lahadi.
Ƙungiyar Arewa ta ce a'a ga kawar da makamai a gefe guda idan babu amincewa
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya sanar da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumin yana kara rashin amincewar kasar da Amurka, kuma kasar ba za ta mika makaman nukiliya ba a irin wannan yanayin.
Ri Yong Ho ya sanar da taron shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki muhimman matakai na nuna kyakkyawar niyyarta a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na makaman nukiliya, rushe wuraren gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin bunkasa makamai da fasahar nukiliya.
"Amma ba mu ga irin wannan amsa daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a amince da tsaronmu na kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayin, ba za a yi watsi da makamai ba da farko a bangarenmu.
Yayin da Ri ya ci gaba da yin korafin da aka sani na Koriya ta Arewa game da juriya ta Washington ga kawar da makaman nukiliya ta hanyar da za a ba da lada ga Koriya ta Arewa yayin da ta ɗauki matakan, sanarwa ta zama mai mahimmanci, tun da bai ƙi jinin kawar da makaman nukiliya ba kamar yadda ya faru da Pyongyang a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne game da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko na shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa da aka gudanar a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin 'yancin nukiliya' na yankin Koriya ta Arewa yayin da Trump ya tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa tun daga lokacin tana neman kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta bayyana cewa dole ne Pyongyang ta fara ajiye makaman nukiliya.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da sassauta tsauraran takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka dauka kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta nace da 'yancin nukiliya' da farko kuma ta kara matsa lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta na tilasta yin amfani da makami, har ma da ta ƙi 'yancin yin wa'azin ƙarshen yaki,' in ji Ri.
