Daliban Harvard suna koyar da darasi game da yadda za su sami isasshen hutawa
A wannan shekara, wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard yana sa dukan daliban su yi barci sosai domin su magance ci gaban al'adun maza na nazarin dare da ke cike da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗaliban jami'a na farko a duniya ba su san ainihin yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Czeisler, malamin likitancin barci a Harvard Medical School kuma masanin asibitin Brigham da Muller, ya tsara wannan hanya, wanda ya yi imanin cewa ita ce ta farko a Amurka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare ta ta fara karatun bayan ta yi jawabi game da tasirin rashin bacci a kan ilmantarwa.
"A ƙarshen makarantar, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, 'Me ya sa ba a gaya mini wannan ba sai yanzu, a shekaruna na ƙarshe?'
Ya ce ba wanda ya gaya masa muhimmancin barci, wanda ya ba ni mamaki", in ji shi.
Wannan darasi, wanda aka fara a wannan shekarar, ya bayyana wa dalibai muhimman abubuwan da suka shafi yadda ake samun barci mai kyau yana taimakawa wajen samun nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyar jiki.
Paul Barreira, Farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma babban darektan kula da lafiyar jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan karatun bayan ta gano cewa ɗalibai suna fama da rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Koyarwar da take da tsawon awa ɗaya tana ɗauke da ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibai ke danna kan kofuna na kofi, da labule, da masu koyarwa, da littattafai don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin yin aiki a lokacin kwanciya.
A wani sashe kuma, an sanar da mahalarta yadda rashin bacci na tsawon lokaci zai iya kara hadarin kamuwa da ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar da ke ɗauke da gumaka masu ma'amala ta ƙarfafa mahalarta su yi tunani a kan rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum.
"Mun san cewa ba za ta canja halin ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun yi imani cewa suna da hakkin sanin wannan bayanin, kamar yadda muke da hakkin sanin irin tasirin da shan taba yake yi a kan lafiyarmu", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Har ila yau, ya ce, al'adar alfahari da yin barci har dare tana nan. Ya kuma ƙara da cewa, fasaha ta zamani da kuma matsin lamba a kan ɗalibai da ke tattare da rashin barci suna daɗa zama matsala.
Tabbatar da isasshen barci da kuma samun kyakkyawan bacci ya kamata ya zama "makamin sirri" na ɗalibi don yaƙar damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, ya ce. Har ma ya guji kiba, saboda rashin bacci yana sa kwakwalwa ta shiga yanayin yunwa, wanda ke sa ta ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, dan California mai shekaru 19 da ke nazarin kimiya da ilimin halitta, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara darasin bayan ya halarci daya daga cikin darussansa a bara a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya buɗe idanunsa kuma ya sa ya yi shirin zuwa makarantar gaba ɗaya.
Mataki na gaba, ka yi tsammani, shi ne a nemi duk daliban digiri na biyu su kammala irin wannan shirin kafin su shiga wata makarantar gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya shawarci ɗalibai su yi la'akari da zaɓin saita ƙararrawa don kwantawa da kuma lokacin da suka farka. Hakazalika, ana ba da shawarar su kasance masu hankali game da tasirin cutarwa na "hasken blue" da fuskokin lantarki da hasken LED ke bayarwa, wanda zai iya lalata yanayin circadian kuma ya haifar da matsalolin barci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Burin Menga ya sa Gerrard ya ci nasara
Rangers sun sha wahala wani mummunan labari lokacin da Dolly Menga ta kai hari ta sa ƙungiyar da ba ta da haɗin kai ta Steven Gerrard ta ci 1-0 a Livingston.
Ibrox ta yi niyyar samun nasarar gida ta farko tun daga 4-1 a watan Fabrairu a St Johnstone, amma Gary Holt ya yi nasarar rasa Gerrard a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, wanda ya bar tawagarsa ta ci gaba da samun maki takwas daga Hearts, shugabannin Ladbrokes Premiership, gasar zakarun Turai.
Menga ya kai hari da minti bakwai kafin hutu kuma wani ranger mai zurfin tunani bai taɓa yin tunanin cewa zai yi kusa ba.
Yayin da Rangers suka sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa matsayi na uku kuma yana bayan Hibernian ne kawai da wata babbar nasara.
Kuma zai iya zama mafi muni ga Rangers bayan da alkalin kotun Calum Spence ya yi fama da rauni a kai bayan da aka yi zargin an jefa shi da wani abu.
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas game da tawagar da ta rushe Ayr a wasan karshe na Betfred Cup, gasar cin kofin League ta Scotland.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya kasance da Livingston 11 wanda ya ci Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda ƙungiyarsa ta yi ta kashe abokan adawarsa a kowane lokaci.
Wataƙila 'yan wasan Rangers sun yi nasara a kan wannan, amma Livingston ya yi nasara sosai a lokacin da suke da ƙwallon ƙafa.
Za su iya yin kwallo a cikin minti biyu kawai lokacin da gajeren lokacin farko na Menga ya tura Scott Pittman zuwa ƙwallon Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan tsakiya ya ɓata wannan babbar dama.
Wani harbi mai ƙarfi daga Keaghan Jacobs ya kai ga Kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma abokin tsaronsa, Alan Lithgow, ya ci shi ne kawai a cikin sanda ta biyu.
'Yan wasan Rangers sun ci gaba da yin nasara, amma sun ga cewa suna da bege fiye da tabbaci game da wasan da suke yi a filin wasa.
Babu shakka, Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa ya kamata su yi bugun jini a minti 15 lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo, amma alkalin wasa, Steven Thomson, ya yi watsi da ikirarin ɗan Colombia.
Rangers sun yi harbi biyu kawai a ƙofar a farkon rabin, amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Ibrox, Liam Kelly, bai sami matsala ba tare da ƙarshen ƙarshen Lassana Coulibaly da kuma bugun Ovie Ejaria.
Duk da yake buɗe Livingston a minti na 34 na iya zama ya saɓa wa ka'idar wasan, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan saboda aikinsu.
Rangers sun sake yin rashin nasara a lokacin da suka fuskanci Jacobs mai karfi.
Scott Arfield bai yi ba yayin da Declan Gallagher ya sanya kwallon ga Scott Robinson, wanda ya riƙe jini mai sanyi don zaɓar Menga don ƙarshen wasa mai sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu yayin da yake canza Coulibaly zuwa Ryan Kent, canji wanda ya yi tasiri kusan nan take lokacin da hagu ya ba da gudummawa ga Morelos, amma mai tsaron gida Kelly ya gudu daga layinsa don toshe shi.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da cinye baƙi ta hanyar yin wasa daidai da irin wasan da suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna tara dogon ball bayan wani.
Ƙungiyar Holt na iya faɗaɗa fa'idar a cikin minti na ƙarshe, amma McGregor ya tashi da kyau don ya ƙi Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya kai daga kusurwar.
Glenn Middleton, wanda ya maye gurbin Rangers, ya nemi karin hukunci a lokacin da ya shiga cikin Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake yin watsi da shi.
Almanac: wanda ya kirkiro Geiger counter
Yanzu kuma shafi na littafinmu na "Sunday Morning": 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekara ce ta 136 da ta wuce, kuma an ƙidaya... ranar haihuwar mai ilimin lissafi mai zuwa Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya don ganowa da kuma auna radiation, wani kirkiro da ya kawo shi ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Daga nan sai ya zama babban masanin kimiyya, Geiger Count ya kuma zama muhimmin ɓangare na al'adun pop, kamar a cikin fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda waɗannan masana kimiyya na cowboy Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka taka rawa:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan a duniya?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne mai ƙididdigar Geiger, wanda ake amfani da shi don gano ma'adinai masu radiation kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin da kwayoyin halitta ke yi a cikin sinadarin da ake amfani da su wajen yin amfani da sinadarin".
Evans: "Ka ce, na tabbata yana tashi yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kadan bayan cika shekaru 63.
Amma abin da ya faru da sunan shi ya tsira.
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa na iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar mutum ya ga ƙwayoyin da ba su da kyau
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa na iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar mutum ya ga ƙwayoyin da ba su da kyau kuma ya kashe su
Alurar rigakafi tana koya wa tsarin garkuwar mutum ganewar kwayoyin da suka lalace a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani
Wannan hanya ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin marasa lafiya, kuma a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje, a canza su.
Za su iya ganin furotin da ke da yawa a cikin nau'ikan cututtukan daji kuma su sake yin allurarsu.
Wani rigakafin gwaji yana nuna sakamako mai kyau ga marasa lafiya da ke fama da ciwon daji.
Wata mace da aka yi wa allurar rigakafi, wadda ke koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki yadda za ta gane ƙwayoyin da ba su da kyau, ta ga ciwon daji na ovarian ta tafi har tsawon watanni 18.
Wannan hanya tana nufin cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin marasa lafiya, kuma a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje, an canza su don su iya "gudu" da furotin da ke da alaƙa da nau'ikan ciwon daji da yawa, wanda ake kira HER2, sannan a ƙi ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky daga Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce, "Bincikenmu ya nuna cewa muna da alurar riga kafi mai ban sha'awa".
Farfesa Berzofsky ya bayyana cewa, HER2 "yana sa ciwon daji na wasu nau'o'in daji ya yi girma", ciki har da na nono, na ovaries, na huhu, da na jikina.
Hanyar da ta yi kama da cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga marasa lafiya kuma ta koya musu su magance ƙwayoyin cuta ta yi aiki a cikin maganin wani nau'in cutar sankarar jini.
Kanye West ya fara jawabinsa na goyon bayan Trump ta hanyar yin hulɗa da shi a cikin wani babban hatsin MAGA (Make America Great Again) bayan ya bayyana a kan shirin Saturday Night Live (SNL).
Kuma sakamakon bai yi kyau ba
A wani shiri na Saturday Night Live, Kanye West ya yi wahayi zuwa gare shi a cikin ɗakin karatu bayan wani gabatarwar da ta rikice inda ya yaba wa shugaban Amurka, Donald Trump, kuma ya ce zai tsaya takara a shekarar 2020.
Bayan ya buga waƙar dare ta uku, mai suna Ghost Town ("Ghost Town"), a cikin abin da ya sa takalmin Make America Great Again, ya soki 'yan Democrat kuma ya sake tabbatar da goyon bayansa ga Trump.
"Na yi magana da fararen fata sau da yawa kuma na ce, 'Yaya za ka so Trump idan yana da wariyar launin fata?'
Idan da na damu da wariyar launin fata, da na bar Amurka tun da daɗewa", in ji shi.
SNL ta fara shirin da satirical satire na Matt Damon, wanda star na Hollywood ya yi wa shaidar Brett Kavanaugh ba'a a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai na Amurka game da karar cin zarafin jima'i da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, Chris Rock ya wallafa hotunan West a shafukan sada zumunta.
Ba a san ko Rock yana ƙoƙarin yin wa West ba'a da wannan labarin ba.
Bugu da ƙari, West ya yi korafi ga masu sauraro cewa ya yi mummunan lokaci a cikin gida saboda hatinsa.
"Sun wuce ni a cikin gida.
Sun ce, 'Kada ka fita da wannan hular.'
Sun tsoratar da ni!
Sai suka ce ina jin zafi", in ji Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba da cewa, "Kana son ganin yadda zan yi?" ya ce, "Zan yi amfani da hatina na Superman, domin yana nufin ba za ka iya gaya mini abin da zan yi ba. Kana son duniya ta ci gaba?
Ka gwada shi da ƙauna".
Kalamansa sun jawo hankalin masu sauraro aƙalla sau biyu kuma 'yan wasan SNL sun bayyana suna jin kunya, ya ruwaito wa mujallar Variety, tare da shaidar da wani da ke wurin ya ba wa jaridar: "Dukan ɗakin karatu ya yi shiru".
Sun sanya West a matsayin magajin karshe na Ariana Grande, wanda tsohon saurayin sa, rapper Mac Miller, ya mutu kwanaki da suka wuce.
West ya ba da labari ga mutane da yawa da yin waƙar "I love it", wanda aka saka kamar kwalban ruwa na Perrier.
West ya samu goyon bayan shugaban kungiyar TPUSA, Candace Turner, wanda ya rubuta wannan sakon a shafinsa na Twitter: "Ga daya daga cikin masu karfin hali: Godiya ga fuskantar Mafia"
Duk da haka, mai gabatar da hirar ta Karen Hunter ta wallafa wani sakon Twitter cewa West kawai "yana zama wanda yake kuma wannan yana da ban mamaki".
