Tauraron Wasannin Mulki Kit Harington ya kai hari ga namiji mai guba
Kit Harington ya fi shahara saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na HBO Game of Thrones.
Dan wasan mai shekara 31 ya yi ta kaiwa ga nuna halin jarumi na maza, yana cewa irin wannan rawar da ake takawa a kan allo tana nufin cewa, sau da yawa, dole ne matasa su kasance masu tsananin hali domin a girmama su.
A wata hira da ta yi da jaridar The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce "wani abu ya kasa" kuma ya yi mamakin yadda za a magance matsalar namiji mai guba a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri Rose Leslie, mai shekara 31, mai yin wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, ta ce tana jin "mai ƙarfi sosai" don magance matsalar.
"Na ji na yi karfi sosai a wannan lokacin. A ina ne muka yi kuskure game da namiji?"
"Me muke koya wa maza sa'ad da suka girma, dangane da matsalar da muke gani yanzu?"
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na ƙara yawan namiji mai guba saboda halayensu na namiji.
Ya ci gaba da cewa: "Mecece halitta ce kuma me ake koyarwa?
Abin da ake koyarwa a talabijin da kuma a kan titi; menene ya sa matasa su ji cewa dole ne su kasance wannan ɓangaren mutum?
Ina ganin wannan na daga cikin manyan tambayoyin zamaninmu; ta yaya za mu canza wannan?
Domin a fili, wani abu ya faru da yaran".
A cikin hira, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani prequel ko sequel na Game of Thrones ba lokacin da jerin suka ƙare a lokacin rani mai zuwa, yana mai cewa "yana da isasshen dawakai da filayen yaƙi".
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai taka rawar gani a cikin wani sabon fim na Sam Shepard, wanda ya ba da labarin wani mai shirya fim da ɗan'uwansa, wanda ɓarawo ne.
A kwanan nan, actor ya bayyana cewa yana ganin cewa ganawarsa da matarsa, Rose, shine mafi kyau na Game of Thrones.
Ya ce: "Na san matata a wannan shirin, don haka, a wata hanya, ta ba ni iyalina na nan gaba da rayuwata daga yanzu".
Rose ta yi aiki a matsayin Ygritte, ƙaunar halin Kit, Jon Snow, a cikin jerin abubuwan da suka lashe Emmy.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yuni na 2018 a ƙasar da ke cikin gidan Leslie, a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sababbin kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar, in ji hukumomin lafiya.
An samu sabbin mutane 40,000 a cikin kashi na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kawai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun gudana ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji daga abin da ya faru a baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta bazu cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon karin jini da aka yi wa mutane.
Amma, yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta hanyar wannan hanyar an rage su kusan zuwa sifili, a cewar jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a kowace shekara, yawan mutanen da ke da HIV ko AIDS a kasar Sin ya karu da 100,000.
Yarda da kwayar cutar HIV ta jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT ta kasar Sin.
An nuna wariya ga 'yan luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma sun ce nuna wariya ga 'yan luwadi ya bazu.
Domin ka'idodin da suka shafi 'yancin kai a kasar, bincike ya nuna cewa tsakanin kashi 70 zuwa 90 na maza da ke yin jima'i da wasu maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka na cutar sun fito ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar shiga duk duniya wajen magance cutar HIV a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
