An kuma fara gina shi ne a kan wani ɗan adam mai ban mamaki da kuma baƙon ɗan sanda na duniya wanda Atkinson ya yi aiki a cikin tallan talabijin da aka manta da su a yanzu na Barclaycard, inda ya haifar da rikici a lokacin da ya wuce.
Akwai wasu lokatai masu kyau a cikin fitowar Johnny English ta ƙarshe.
