Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy sun ba da rahoton cewa binciken da FBI ta yi game da Kavanaugh zai iya sa su canja ra'ayinsu
Binciken FBI game da zargin da aka yi wa Alkalin Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta akalla mako guda don kada kuri'ar karshe game da nadin sa a Kotun Koli.
A ranar Lahadi, a wata hira da aka yi da jaridar "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi Sanatocin Republican John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko FBI za ta iya fitar da wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya nuna cewa ya fi abokinsa a South Carolina bude baki.
"Ina nufin, ba shakka", ya ce Kennedy.
"Na ce zan je wurin shari'ar. Na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira bayan da aka gabatar da kara kuma na tambaye ta ko ta yi hakan.
Ya kasance mai ƙarfi, mai ƙuduri, mai ƙarfi".
Duk da haka, muryar Graham ta zama kamar ba za a iya canja ta ba.
"Abin da na yi game da Brett Kavanaugh ya tabbata kuma zan yi zargin da ya yi fashewa", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba; amma na san wannan: Brett ya ƙaryata shi", in ji Graham da nufin Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma mutanen da ka ambata ba su iya tabbatar da shi.
Wannan ya faru shekaru 36 da suka wuce.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu".
Menene bikin Global Citizen Festival kuma ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke dauke da wasu manyan taurari da ke shirin yin aiki da kuma wani manufa mai ban mamaki, wato kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Global Citizen zai ga dubban mutane suna zuwa wurin sandstone a Great Lawn na Central Park, ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon kamar na Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawar da talauci kafin 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ce ta kasa da kasa da ke neman kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da shi.
