Jihohi 18 da kuma gundumar Columbia sun kalubalanci sabon manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi goma sha takwas da kuma gundumar Columbia sun amince da a shigar da kara a kotu dangane da sabuwar manufar Amurka ta ba da mafaka ga wadanda ke gudun gudun gudun hijira daga tashin hankali a gida ko kuma kungiyoyin aikata laifi.
A ranar Juma'a, wakilan jihohi 18 da kuma gundumar sun gabatar da rahoto mai kyau ga kotun a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka da ke kalubalantar siyasa, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan wanda ya shigar da kara a cikin shari'ar Sessions de Grace v. da American Civil Liberties Union ta gabatar a watan Agusta a kan manufofin tarayya ba.
Ta ce maigidanta "da 'ya'yanta da ke cikin wata ƙungiya ta aikata laifi" sun yi mata fyade, amma jami'an Amurka sun ƙi takardar neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
Ka tsare ta a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, wadanda ke samar da yawan masu neman mafaka zuwa Amurka, a matsayin al'ummai da ke fuskantar matsalolin da suka shafi kungiyoyin laifi da kuma tashin hankali na gida.
Sabon manufar baƙi ta Amurka ta soke wani hukunci na 2014 na Hukumar Kula da Kararrakin Shige da Fice da ke ba da izinin baƙi marasa takaddama da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na gida su nemi mafaka.
Babban lauya na gundumar Columbia, Karl Racine, ya ce a wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabon manufar "ba ta da alaka da dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na duniya na shekaru da yawa".
"Kundin tarayya ya bukaci a yi amfani da duk wani takardar neman mafaka bisa ga ainihin abubuwan da suka faru da kuma yanayin da ake nema, kuma wannan haramcin ya keta wannan ka'idar", in ji rahoton abokantaka na kotun.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ci gaba da jayayya a cikin rahoton cewa manufofin da ke hana shigowar baƙi suna cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna bayyana cewa suna iya zama 'yan kasuwa kuma suna "ba da ma'aikata".
A watan Yuni, Babban Shari'a Jeff Sessions ya umurci alƙalan da ke kula da shige da fice su daina ba da mafaka ga wadanda suka tsere wa zalunci a gida da kuma tashin hankali daga kungiyoyin masu aikata laifi.
"Ana samun mafaka ga waɗanda suka bar ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoro saboda tseren, addini, ƙasa ko kuma suna cikin wani rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwar siyasa a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa yin amfani da mafaka don magance duk matsalolin (har da duk matsalolin da suka fi tsanani) da mutane ke fuskanta a kowace rana a duniya ba.
