Duk wannan ya sa wannan ajiyar bayanan sirri ta zama na musamman shine mai amfani yana da cikakken iko akan wanda zai iya samun damar wane bayani.
Kamfanin ya bayyana hakan a matsayin "karfafawa ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar shugabanta John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya ba da albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewa masu dacewa don taimakawa sanya Solid a duniya.
A halin yanzu, Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani kamfanin tsaro na IBM, wasu masu haɓaka da aka yi hayar su don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shiryen aikin sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu tasowa a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu na rarraba tare da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi ko tawagarsa ba su tattauna da "Facebook ko Google ba game da ko za su gabatar da cikakken canji wanda zai canza tsarin kasuwancin su daga rana zuwa rana.
"Ba mu bukatar izinin ku".
A wata kasida da aka wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "aikin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizo na Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet ta hanyar kafa ƙungiyar World Wide Web Consortium a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya zama babbar murya a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na cibiyar sadarwa.
Har yanzu, yayin da Inrupt ke gudana, Berners-Lee ya ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma ya jagoranci ƙungiyar World Wide Web Consortium, da kuma Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da tabbaci sosai game da wannan sabon zamani na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Abin girmamawa ga Bernard Vann, wani limami da aka ba da lambar yabo ta Victoria a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
Firist na Ikilisiyar Ingila ne kaɗai da aka ba da Victoria Cross a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya ya sami ladabi a gidansa bayan shekaru 100.
Lt. Col. da Rev. Bernard Vann an ba shi lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a cikin hari na Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, an kashe shi ne ta hanyar harbi kwanaki hudu bayan haka ba tare da sanin cewa an ba shi lambar yabo mafi girma ta soja ta Birtaniya ba.
A ranar Asabar, jikokinta biyu ne suka gano wani abin tunawa a cikin girmamawa a cikin wani gangami a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Ɗan jikoki Michael Vann ya nuna alamar gano wannan abin tunawa shekaru 100 bayan da kakarsa ya ba shi wannan sunan.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta hanyar tashar Saint-Quentin "ta hanyar hazo mai yawa da kuma ƙarƙashin wutar bindigogi mai tsanani", in ji The London Gazette.
Daga baya ya yi hanzari ya isa layin wuta kuma, tare da "babban ƙarfin hali", ya jagoranci layin gaba kafin ya yi hanzari tare da bindiga kuma ba tare da taimakon kowa ba, kuma ya kashe mutane uku daga rundunar abokan gaba.
Lt. Col. Vann an kashe shi ne ta hanyar wani dan wasan Jamus a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wata daya kafin yakin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da kakansa ya yi "wani abu ne da ba zan taɓa iya rayuwa da shi ba, amma ko da yake darasi ne".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vann sun kuma sanya kambi na furanni bayan bikin, wanda ya jagoranci ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial.
Michael Vann ya ce yana "girmamawa sosai da ya halarci wannan bikin" kuma ya kara da cewa "karfin wannan jarumi na gaske ya nuna goyon bayan mutane da yawa".
Peppa Pig ta yanke wa magoya bayan MMA a mafi kyawun lokacin
Ka yi tunanin kana yin dare da dare kana jin daɗin cikakken wasan kwaikwayon Bellator 206, kuma a lokacin da mafi kyawun ɓangaren ya zo wani abu mai kyau ya hana ka.
San Jose ta ƙunshi gwagwarmayar gwagwarmaya 13, shida daga cikinsu manyan gwagwarmaya ne, kuma ana watsa su kai tsaye a Burtaniya a tashar Channel 5.
Amma da ƙarfe shida na safe, daidai lokacin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald suke shirin yin hira, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamaki lokacin da suka ga Peppa Pig ta fito.
Wasu ba su yi mamaki ba bayan sun yi sa'o'i da yawa suna jiran ganin gwagwarmayar.
Wani mai sha'awar wasan kwaikwayo ya bayyana sauyawar zuwa wadannan zane-zanen yara a shafinsa na Twitter a matsayin "dabara mai ban dariya".
"Ka'idojin jihar sun ce wannan abun bai dace da karfe 6 na safe ba, saboda haka sai an canza shi zuwa shirye-shiryen yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, babban mataimakin shugaban kasuwanci da sadarwa na Bellator, lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da sake watsa shirye-shiryen.
"Peppa Pig, shi ne cewa".
Scott Coker, shugaban Bellator, ya ce za su yi la'akari da masu kallo na Burtaniya a shirye-shiryen su na gaba.
"Ina tsammanin za mu iya magance shi idan muka yi tunani game da maimaitawa", in ji Coker.
"Amma idan karfe shida na safe ne a can, ba za mu iya warware matsalar ba sai ranar Lahadi, wanda zai zama Litinin a gare su.
Amma muna aiki don samun mafita.
Da na samu canji, sai na soma samun saƙonni da yawa, kuma ba duka ba ne masu kyau.
Mun yi kokarin gyara shi domin mun yi tunanin cewa kuskure ne na fasaha.
Amma ba haka ba ne, matsalar gwamnati ce.
Na yi alkawari ba zai sake faruwa ba.
Za mu yi yaki biyar maimakon shida. Muna so mu ba da mafi kyau ga magoya bayanmu, amma za mu wuce kuma mu yi wasa da juna.
Ya yi mana mummunan fushi".
Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji kasawa saboda jima'i
Dan wasan Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin kamar bai fi kowa ba saboda jima'i, amma hakan ya sa ya sami dalilin yin nasara.
Wannan ɗan wasan mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci cewa ba kowa ba ne yake kama da shi ba sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare.
A lokacin da ya halarci shirin farko na Radio 4 na Desert Island Discs wanda Lauren Laverne ta jagoranci, ya bayyana cewa ya fara magana game da 'yancin' yan luwadi don ba da bege ga wasu.
Ta kuma ce zama uba ya taimaka mata ta daidaita muhimmancin lashe gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, mai gabatar da wannan shirin, ta yi rashin lafiya.
Da yake baƙon shirin farko da Laverne ya gabatar, Daley ya ce yana jin "ƙananan" ga sauran mutane domin "ba a yarda da zamantakewar jama'a ba cewa kuna son yara".
Ta ce: "Har wa yau, wannan jin cewa ni ba na kowa ba ne ya motsa ni kuma ya ba ni ƙarfin da nake bukata don in yi nasara".
Yana so ya nuna cewa shi "wani ne" don kada mutane su ji kunya idan sun gano jima'i.
Ta lashe lambar tagulla biyu a gasar Olympics, ta zama babbar mai ba da agaji ga LGBT kuma ta yi amfani da bayyanarta a wasannin Commonwealth na Ostiraliya don neman ƙarin ƙasashe su kawar da cin zarafin luwadi.
Ya yanke shawarar yin magana domin yana jin yana da sa'a don ya iya rayuwa a fili kuma ba tare da tsoron sakamakon ba, kuma yana so ya ba da bege ga wasu.
Dan wasan duniya na sau uku ya ce ya yi sha'awar dan wasan Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013, "ya zama abin mamaki".
Daley ta auri wannan wanda ya lashe kyautar Oscar a bara kuma ta ce shekaru 20 da suka yi a tsakaninsu ba su taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan kana rayuwa a cikin wannan ɗan gajeren lokaci" (ta halarci wasannin Olympics a lokacin da ta kai shekara 14 kuma mahaifinta ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka), yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya da ya taɓa fuskantar irin wannan tashin hankali.
A watan Yuni, ma'auratan sun haifi ɗansu na farko, Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma wannan haihuwar ta sa Daley ya canja ra'ayinsa gaba ɗaya.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, babban abin da ya motsa ni shi ne in lashe lambar zinare", in ji ta.
"Amma yanzu na san cewa akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinariya ta Olympics muhimmanci.
A gare ni, lambar yabo ita ce Robbie".
Ɗansa ya kira mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekara 40 a kan kansa na kwakwalwa.
Mahaifin Daley bai yarda da cewa za ta mutu ba, kuma abu na karshe da ya tambayi ɗansa shi ne tikiti zuwa London 2012, yana so ya kasance a gaba.
"Ban gaya masa ba cewa ba zan kasance a nan don yin layin farko ba", in ji Daley.
Ya ƙara da cewa: "Ina riƙe da hannunsa sa'ad da ya daina numfashi kuma a wannan lokacin, sa'ad da ya mutu, na fahimci cewa ba zan iya cin nasara ba".
A shekara ta gaba, Daley ya yi gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe lambar tagulla.
"A lokacin ne na fahimci cewa wannan shi ne burina na rayuwa: tsalle a gaban taron a ƙasarmu a gasar Olympics, babu abin da ya fi wannan jin daɗi", in ji ta.
Zaɓin Proud na Heather Small ba shi da kyau, tun da yake shi ne waƙar da ta bi shi yayin da yake shirya don gasar Olympics kuma har yanzu tana sa gashinsa ya zama mai ƙyama.
Desert Island Discs a tashar BBC Radio 4, a ranar Lahadi da ƙarfe 11:15 na yammacin duniya.
Wani Mickelson mai rauni ya ƙare a kan benci na Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47 a ranar Lahadi, amma zai yi aiki sosai don kada ya zama abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda ke halartar taron na shekara-shekara na 12, ya sauka a benci bisa shawarar Kyaftin Jim Furyk kuma bai iya shiga wasan fourball ko foursomes na Asabar ba.
Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar aikin, kamar yadda ya faru a wasu lokutan da yawa a Amurka, gwarzon sau biyar ya yi amfani da rana don ƙarfafawa da aiki don inganta motsinsa.
Ko da yake bai taɓa zama mai ƙwarewa ba, har ma a lokacin da ya fi tsayi a cikin aikinsa, a cikin shekaru 48 bai dace da filin Le Golf National mai kyau ba, inda tsayi mai tsayi yakan hukunta harbi mara kyau.
Kuma idan hakan bai isa ba, Mickelson zai yi karo da dan wasan na tara a ranar Lahadi, mai suna Francesco Molinari, wanda ya lashe gasar cin kofin Birtaniya, wanda ya hada da Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni hudu na wannan makon.
Idan 'yan Amirkawa, da suka kai maki hudu a farkon wasannin guda 12, suka fara da kyau, aikin Mickelson zai iya zama da muhimmanci sosai.
Furyk ya amince da mijinta, ko da yake ba zai iya faɗi wani abu ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci matsayina sosai, ya yi mini ta'aziyya, ya miƙa mini hannu, ya ce zan kasance a shirye gobe.
"Ya amince da kansa sosai.
Ya yi fice a cikin gidan wasan kwaikwayon kuma ya ba da gudummawa sosai ga 'yan wasan a makon da ya gabata da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban yi tunanin zan buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tunanin zan yi wasa da yawa, amma a ƙarshe, wannan shine yadda abubuwa suke, kuma wannan shine yadda muke tsammanin ya kamata ya kasance.
Kamar kowa, yana son zama a waje".
A ranar Lahadi Mickelson zai ci rikodin Nick Faldo a kan yawan wasannin da aka buga a gasar Ryder Cup.
Zai iya kammala gasar cin kofin Ryder, wadda ba ta taɓa kaiwa ga matakin da ya samu ba.
Mickelson yana da nasara 18, 20 da kuma 7 a raga, ko da yake Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa yana ba da kyauta ga tawagar.
"Yana da ban dariya, mai ba'a, mai basira kuma yana son yin hulɗa da mutane, yana da kyau mutum ya kasance a cikin tawagar", in ji shi.
"Ina son ganin yadda 'yan wasan matasa suka yi masa wannan makon.
Yana da yawa fiye da a mai kyau player".
Kyaftin na Turai, Thomas Bjorn, yana tsoron cewa za a rasa fa'idar
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Turai, ya san daga kwarewa cewa samun babban fa'ida a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup na iya zama tafiya mai wuya.
Dan Danish din ya fara wasa a shekara ta 1997 a wasan Valderrama, inda wani rukuni da Seve Ballesteros ya jagoranci ya kasance yana da maki biyar a kan Amurkawa, amma sun ƙare har zuwa layin karshe tare da ƙaramin nasara 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Ka ci gaba da tunanin cewa muna da babbar fa'ida a Valderrama; kamar yadda muke a Brookline, inda muka rasa, amma a Valderrama mun ci kaɗan", Bjorn ya yi tunani, a cikin hoto, bayan kallon ci gaban 2018 ya ci 5-3 a ranar Jumma'a da kuma, jiya, 10-6 a Le Golf National.
Tarihi ya nuna cewa wannan ba ya ƙare.
Dole ne in tafi don su duka gobe.
Dole ne ka fita ka yi abin da ya dace.
Wannan ba zai ƙare ba har sai an sami maki a cikin alamar.
Manufarmu ita ce mu lashe wannan kofin, kuma dole ne mu mai da hankali ga hakan.
Ba zan gaji da cewa ba, na mayar da hankali ne ga 'yan wasanmu 12 da suke tare da mu, amma kuma na san abin da ke tare da mu: 'yan wasan duniya mafi kyau. "
Bjorn ya yi farin ciki da yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi a filin golf mai wuya, ya kara da cewa: "Ba zan taɓa yin waƙa ba kafin lokacin.
Da safe za mu fuskanci wata dabba.
Gobe rana ce ta nuna nuna bambanci, kuma a can ma dole ne mu nuna cewa muna da daraja.
Yana da kyau ka kasance tare da abokin tarayya a lokacin da abubuwa suka yi kyau, amma idan ka fuskanci abubuwa a kan mutum, to, ka gwada ka iyawa a matsayin golfer.
