Furyk kansa ya kasance a ƙarshen biyu na waɗannan ra'ayoyin ranar ƙarshe, yana cikin ƙungiyar da ta ci nasara a Brookline, amma ya ƙare a matsayin mai asara bayan mu'ujiza ta Turai a Medinah. "
