Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar majiyoyin hukuma, sun yi sanadiyyar mutuwar akalla mutane 384, wanda ake sa ran zai ci gaba da karuwa.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu bayanai masu muhimmanci game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu babban birnin lardin Celebes Central ne, wanda ke kusa da ƙarshen wani kusurwar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Celebes, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ke kan iyakar kilomita 300 na arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Celebes.
Wannan yanki, yanki ne na gudanarwa wanda ba shi da lardin, yana da yawan mutane kusan 299,200 a cikin shekara ta 2017.
Fishing da noma sune manyan ginshiƙai na tattalin arzikin lardin Celebes ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ana yin ma'adinai na nickel a lardin, amma suna da yawa a Morowali, a gefen tekun Celebes.
Palu da Donggala sun sha wahala daga tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Rage Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya kuma shafi yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, wanda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan Tekun Fuskar Pacific mai yawan girgizar ƙasa, saboda haka tana fama da girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar kasa mai tsanani a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin Sumatra, da ta faru a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14, ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su, a Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin ƙasa mai ƙarfi ya afkawa yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, tsibirin da aka fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya lalata gabar kudu, ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar kusan mutane 700.
2009: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 a kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, wanda ke kusa da Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata dubban al'ummomi kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai sauƙi ta shafi mulkin Pidie Jaya, dake Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici, yayin da mutane suka tuna da lalacewar da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004 suka haifar.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 suka mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: An yi manyan girgizar ƙasa a tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, wanda ya kashe mutane sama da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin gidaje na wucin gadi.
