Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman yin amfani da hukuncin kisa da aka yi amfani da shi sau da yawa ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York na kokarin yanke hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a yi amfani da shi a jihar ba tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan titin keke a kan titin West Side Highway na Lower Manhattan, yana kashe ma'aikatan da kuma masu hawa keke da ya tarar a hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe "da gangan" kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar a Kananan Hukumomin New York.
Dukkanin laifuffuka biyu sun shafi yiwuwar yin amfani da hukuncin kisa bisa ga takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, wani juriyar tarayya ta gabatar da zargin Saipov kan laifuffuka 22, ciki har da laifuffuka takwas na kisan kai tare da ƙungiyar aikata laifuka, aikin da masu gabatar da kara ke amfani da shi a lokuta na aikata laifuka, da kuma laifin tashin hankali da lalata motocin mota.
An yi amfani da "shirye-shiryen da aka yi da kyau" don kai hari, in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi "m, mummunan da kuma lalata" harin.
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asarar iyalan da abokai Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco" kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sanarwar niyyar tuhuma.
