A cikin shekaru goma da suka gabata, Kudancin Gundumar New York ba ta gudanar da shari'ar kisa ba.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan masu safarar miyagun ƙwayoyi biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai a watan Satumba na 2009.
A shekarar 1953, an yi wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a wani shari'ar tarayya a birnin New York, wanda aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa bisa laifin yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
